Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}は？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We are no different from the Ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:12.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これからは 「ネフェルピトー」って呼んでね。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:12.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No... We are far worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:47.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全師団長　兵隊長に告ぐ 全師団長　兵隊長に告ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:47.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The poison, which spread \Nwhen the rose bloomed, was superior to similar toxins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:55.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これより軍団長ネフェルピトー殿 立ち会いの下 第一講堂において 授与式を執り行う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:55.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}because it was immediately absorbed by \Nthose in the area unfortunate enough to survive the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:02:01.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフっ。 そこで諸君らは 多少の苦痛と引き換えに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:02:01.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rapid destruction of their organs would begin, and their bodies themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:09.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}莫大なパワーを得ることになる。 その力　遺憾なく 女王様のために発揮せよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:09.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}would become poisons that continued to \Nemit new poison, until the victim died. The amount of poison for a lethal dose and \Nthe amount of time until the subject died
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:33.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らは真っすぐ進んでる。 この先にキメラアントの 巣があるとみて間違いない。 すげぇな。 あれから一瞬も外さずに ずっと捉え続けてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:33.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In other words, it was a demonic weapon \Nmore inhumane than any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:58.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　ゲームをクリアした後 カイトに会わせたのも…。 ジン！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:58.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Word x Is x That Someone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジンがカイトと俺達を 会わせた後のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どれだけ予測していたかは 分からない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What is happening to my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:24.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}きっと　ゴンも気に入るってことは 確信してたはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:24.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pouf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:34.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　絶対　カイトに ついて行くだろうってことも。 「カイトと一緒に旅をして もっと強くなれ」ってことだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:34.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is something the matter, Meruem-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:41.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}修行の場にしちゃ かなりシビアだけどな。 だからこそ　俺は　お前達に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:41.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Have you changed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:45.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何度も覚悟を問うて来た。 あっ。 あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:45.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In that case, we must evacuate you at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:56.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}前に　お前達が言った通り ジンさんは　俺に何かを期待して お前達を 託したのかもしれない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:56.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your Majesty? Even when I can see right through him, he still refuses to divulge his secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:04.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが俺は　お前達をこの旅で 鍛え上げようなんて思ってない。 そんな余裕もない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:04.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Very well. I only have to capture the remaining intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:11.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　お前達が使えると 思ったから連れて来ただけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:11.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am very curious about your secret now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:14.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あとは　お前達自身の覚悟の問題。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:14.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You do not intend to change your \Nmind about telling me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:24.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}覚悟があれば　「念」も上達するし 戦いにも強くなるだろう。 逆に　そうならねば アリに食われて死ぬだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:24.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I will keep my word, even if it costs me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　死ぬわけにはいかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:43.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　「ハンター十ヶ条」の 其乃一にも 厳然と定められている。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:43.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's already using his final \Npermissible En search!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:49.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}狩りとは 狙った者と狙われた者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:49.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:52.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}互いの覚悟のぶつかり合いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:52.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}everything. I see what has changed since \Nthe first time I used En.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:57.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}互いに覚悟を持って　ぶつけ合い 勝敗を決するのが狩りだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:57.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The footprints that were not there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:04.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}負ければ 相手のおきてやルールに従い 多くの場合　命を奪われる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:04.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An abandoned vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ルール…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Youpi's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが嫌なら勝つしかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A door that has been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:15.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」の上達は　もちろん 敵を知り　己を知ることこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:15.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And someone responding to my \NEn who did not previously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:23.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　だから　あの時カイトは 俺を殴ってくれたんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:23.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヘビブナの群生地に 入る奴があるか！))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Was it you who killed Youpi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:40.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((見ろ　子連れのキツネグマが残す 縄張のシグナルだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:40.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A-Absolutely not! I am a mere Squadron Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:46.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((これを見たら どんな　のんきな動物も 隣山まで逃げるほど ヤバいもんだ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:46.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I would never have any reason to kill Youpi-dono! Youpi-dono
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:51.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれも森のおきて ルールだもんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:51.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was talking to me when he \Nsuddenly coughed up blood, became overcome with pain, and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:57.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジンに代わって ルールを教えてくれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:57.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I swear that I'm not lying! I'm not lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:10.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…。 ん？ ん？ そうだ　思い出した。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:10.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But before he could answer my question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハンターライセンス？ これは？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:21.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジンさんのだ。 えっ　ジンの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:21.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe that he must have been hit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:26.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の最終試験の課題 覚えているか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:26.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}by some sort of attack before encountering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:30.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　ジンを捜し当てること。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:30.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's why I came here to \Ninvestigate if any intruders
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その試験が始まる前に ジンさんに渡されたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}are hidden in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:38.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「こいつを使って 俺を捜してみろ」ってな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:38.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Royal Guard Pouf...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:47.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ジンさんを捜し当てた時 返そうと思ったんだが…。 え？　受け取らなかったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:47.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's going to be trouble. I'm pretty sure he has the \Nability to read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:51.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　今の今まで忘れてた。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:51.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Welfin is a serious threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ…。 んが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have no idea what he might tell the King...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:57.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン　お前　ジンさんは 自分で捜すって言ってたよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:57.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Simply telling him to keep quiet \Nwould be too lenient. I should eliminate him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:03.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ…　うん。 ならば　必ず捜し出せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:03.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I should accuse him of being a traitor, \Nand execute him on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　お前から そいつを返しておいてくれないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In any case, I must get him away from the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:11.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　まずは　カイトと一緒に この仕事をやり遂げて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:11.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Meruem-sama, he is—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もっともっと強くなってから…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I know what you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:19.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そしたら必ず　ジンを見つけて これを返すよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:19.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can now sense the emotions of \Nany that my En has touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:23.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}約束する。 頼んだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:23.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I could feel his unbridled hostility toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:28.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さぁ　先を急ぐぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:28.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In... Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らを見失う。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once someone has been exposed to my En, I can see into their mind by simply looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:40.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おら！ 次！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:40.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So it wasn't just Youpi's wings and attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}凡夫って大変だな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King also inherited my Spiritual Message...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:48.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こんな面倒なことしなきゃ 能力を引き出せないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:48.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And he's made it infinitely more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ペギー　あとを頼むね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King is invincible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どちらへ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:58.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The King is unrivaled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:03.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確かめて来る 僕が　どれだけ強いか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:03.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And yet... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}化け物だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why is my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何てことだ　信じられん。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}filled with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:17.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうしたの？　カイト。 ゴン　キルア　すぐ逃げろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:17.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}such unease?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}え？ え？ 早く行け　ここから離れろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now there is some fear mixed in, but there is no concealing \Nyour desire to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見っけた。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}what drives your hatred of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:40.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺から離れろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:40.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ！ あ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is no time to let emotion \Nget the better of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}う…。 う…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You must follow the proper order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:20.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。 うぁ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:20.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He has deep ties to my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バッ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, he does not realize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いい判断だ　キルア。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you continue questioning him, it is very likely that he will reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アッハッハッハ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe that you would not want your reward before winning the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:53.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶体絶命のピンチだな。 いい目が出ろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:53.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I will keep my secret hidden using only truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:59.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ドゥルルル…　３。 へぇ　そんなこともできるの。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:59.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you wish to continue our contest, I believe you should wait to question him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達は　うぬぼれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I should have run away right off the bat. Temptation got the better of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:40.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２人合わせて 片腕を失ったカイト以下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:40.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When I saw the giant Youpi \Nshrunken down like some bug, and then he dropped dead, I actually had the delusion that I could be King... So I stayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴は　そう判断した
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was drunk on my delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:46.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが現実
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:46.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I felt almighty, like some sheltered little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:53.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　カイト１人なら こんなことにはならなかった くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:53.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I felt alive. Yeah, I'm an idiot! I was drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達は　大バカだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Too many things happened simultaneously, \Nand then I remembered Gyro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:44.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:44.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What tools do I have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The message? Pouf's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:58.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ　ハァ…。 [TEL]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:58.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will it be enough to save me? What do I say? The first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:02.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハァ　ハァ…。 [TEL]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:02.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The first word I say is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:12.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ　カイトを 置いて来た!?　一体どうして！ 一体どういうこと？ 何でか　ちゃんと説明して！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:12.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just one word will decide \Nwhether I live or die. If I choose the wrong one, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:20.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　分かった とにかく　そこで待ってて。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:20.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This overwhelming pressure. This abnormal tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕達も　ちょうど そっちに向かってるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:24.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pouf, does that secret
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}without waiting for Pouf to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ネテロ会長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Despite the understanding that he \Nhad Pouf's unwavering loyalty, the murderous aura visibly \Nemanating from the King
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だ　ガキじゃねえか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}indicated that Pouf would have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:23.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}物見遊山で首突っ込むから やけどするんだよ。 さっさと　お家に帰んな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:23.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}but to atone with his death if that answer \Nwas not what the King wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}かわいそうでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}were equally meaningless before the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:36.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手は　ただの子供なんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:36.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No one could stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:44.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホッホッホ…！ 随分と　ヘコんでおるのぉ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:44.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even then, I was already
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:50.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんなに敵は　手ごわかったか？ くっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:50.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:59.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」を使える奴がいた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:59.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to my own loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:05.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今まで会った誰よりも 薄気味悪いオーラだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:05.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There is nothing that I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}兄貴より。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Though the contest has yet to conclude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分で「念」を覚えてみて よく分かる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That is all there is to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:31.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんた達も　すごく強い。 それでも　あいつに 勝てる気がしない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:31.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His incredible resolve and madness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}stopped the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:48.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}君は今　一種のパニック状態に 陥っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:48.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:54.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あとは私達に任せて ゆっくりベッドで休むことですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:54.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:16:00.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッハッハ…！ 言ってることは 俺と一緒じゃねえかよ　ノヴ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:16:00.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Welfin immediately understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}坊ず　念使い同士の戦いに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am going to be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:16.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前は　ずれてるんだよ。 相手の能力が　どんなものか 分からないのが普通。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:16.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One second later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:20.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ほんの一瞬の緩み　怯みが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:20.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:28.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一発逆転の致命傷になる。 一見したオーラの総量が 多い少ないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:28.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Upon learning his fate, Welfin instantly appeared \Nto age one hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気休めにもならねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:40.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝敗なんて たゆたってて当たり前。 それが「念」での戦闘。 だが　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:40.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was when his past rapidly \Nflashed through his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１００％勝つ気でやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:44.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}and then scattered, the fragments \Nmingling with his present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:48.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが念使いの気概ってもんさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:48.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One word...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:53.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}相手のオーラに気おされ 逃げた時点で　お前は失格。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:53.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My first and last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:57.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敗者以下だ。 モラウ　もういい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:57.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Caught between the desire to live \Nand unavoidable death...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンは　寝とるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One word...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:07.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵を攻撃しようとしたから 腕ずくで止めた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:07.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The message for the King! One word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:12.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}手加減する余裕なかったから いつ目が覚めるか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:12.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What Pouf discussed with Pitou! One word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:16.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッハッハ　そっちの坊ずは まだ見込みがあるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:16.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pouf's secret! One word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}モラウ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:24.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}巨大キメラアントが 人を食うという信じ難い話。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:24.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}One word! ...won't die until I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:36.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}事実である以上 全力で被害拡大を防がねばならぬ。 中途半端な戦力は 敵に吸収される恐れがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:36.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As his brain cells began working \Nharder than ever before, he made a choice that he never would \Nhave in normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Komugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:18.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((相手のオーラに気おされ 逃げた時点で　お前は失格))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:18.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He values her more than I feared. Punish me for my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は…　失格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No words are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア。 あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We are one now. There will be no punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I never had a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:42.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だよ　「ありがとう」って。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:42.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Continue searching for Pitou. The two captured intruders \Nmay have information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:47.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺を止めてくれたの キルアだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:47.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once you are done, release them. I have nothing else to ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:52.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あのまま俺が暴走してたら カイトの邪魔してた。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:52.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All I can do is nod.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:58.60,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうすれば　３人とも危なかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:58.60,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes. The opened door...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:04.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　俺はカイトを見殺しにした。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:04.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And footprints leading inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カイトは生きてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The resolve of the two that I sensed with my En.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:09.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あんな奴には　絶対
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:09.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All signs lead to one conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.11,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対に負けない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.11,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Welfin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:18.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　あれだけのケガ 奴を倒しても　すぐには動けず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:18.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Y-Yes! Komugi is in the underground warehouse \Nwith the woman and the octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どこかに身を潜めて待ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:21.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your job was to deliver that information \Nto me or the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達が戻って来るのを。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}H-How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　早く戻ろう　強くなって。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I believe the octopus was the \Nreason you accepted this job. There was a different reason \Nwhy you did not complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カイトを助けに！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is that reason the cause of your hatred for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So it is. Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:52.10,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前は光だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:52.10,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once you answer my question, \Nyou are free to go wherever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:08.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}時々　まぶし過ぎて 真っすぐ見られないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:08.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They said that they're waiting in Bizeff's \Nprivate courtyard, in Area D.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.61,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.61,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gyro is the only man I'll ever call King! You... All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}強くなって。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are enemies! Our enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:40.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}城に冷凍庫を用意せよ
